workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
When it comes to your back and biceps, these moves are classics for a reason: they get results!


Nail the new lifts with the tutorial before starting. Up your weights when you're confident, but don't let your form slide.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Prime your body to lift at your best.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: The wide grip puts the focus on your upper back.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: You can add weight if these reps are feeling too easy.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: These rows will fast track your pull-up power by targeting the same muscles.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Finish with big reps for your back and arms.
